    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337650/extras/7a4f68649650f6a866e51669132f38da.poster.avif?t=1744825156\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337650/extras/7a4f68649650f6a866e51669132f38da.webm?t=1744825156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337650/extras/7a4f68649650f6a866e51669132f38da.mp4?t=1744825156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>氛围恐怖：</strong> 《CURFEW》提供的恐怖体验超越了简单的惊吓。游戏强调打造紧张而诡异的氛围，让您在整个旅程中紧绷神经。<br><br></li><li><strong>潜行与策略：</strong> 您必须依靠潜行来生存。绕过守卫、利用干扰并策划您的行动，以避开每个角落潜伏的危险。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337650/extras/d157c67d790966046a0b95ca0cb23667.poster.avif?t=1744825156\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337650/extras/d157c67d790966046a0b95ca0cb23667.webm?t=1744825156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337650/extras/d157c67d790966046a0b95ca0cb23667.mp4?t=1744825156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>末日开放世界：</strong> 探索一个被政府压迫和神秘瘟疫笼罩的恐怖开放世界。揭开古老的秘密，探索废弃城镇和垂死文明的废墟。<br><br></li><li><strong>以叙事为驱动：</strong> 展示复杂阴谋的层层剥离，这些阴谋威胁着社会的根基。揭示瘟疫起源的古老真相，政府的角色以及人类的潜在救赎。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337650/extras/230a7414bf2bbd97cfe4aba8164c6254.poster.avif?t=1744825156\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item